column5: I've been having some serious bad days lately... just got a flat tire yesterday.. got it fixed today in the morning and was bored as heck, so i went to the river for a few casts sorry for the bad quality =P  k here's a re-upload =]
So what does the plastic surgeon say?
Well I'm glad you caught a fish, and a nice one at that.  Edit:  Thanks for changing it, that is much better
Is this a picture of your flat tire with a silver nail in it, or a fish?
lol~ a friend told me about this spot and i'm not sure if he'd like it if i don't blur out the background
nice fish.....  catching a decent fish always turns a bad day in to a good one for me too
It doesnt look like the Credit River to me ...  Nice fish...good on ya ..
well, now that you fixed the pic, nice fish
